    File.ReadAllText(@"C:\TestData\orders.csv"));
```

**Problem:** Depends on a hard-coded file at `C:\TestData\orders.csv`. This test will fail on any machine that doesn't have that file (CI, Linux, any teammate's computer). Also qualifies as **Resource Optimism** — it assumes the file exists without checking.

**Fix:** Inline the test data:

